Mauritius Central Bank Rates Biggest Lenders ‘Satisfactory’ in New Tests

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-03-31T12:26:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-31/mauritius-central-bank-rates-biggest-lenders-satisfactory-in-new-tests.html
Mauritius’s central bank rated
 Mauritius Commercial Bank (MCB) , the nation’s biggest lender, and the
 State Bank of Mauritius Ltd. (SBM)  as “satisfactory” in new
financial tests, the Bank of Mauritius said.  The ratings look at commercial banks’ capital, asset
quality, management, earnings and liquidity, the Port Louis-
based  central bank said in a statement on its website today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gordon Bell at 
 gbell16@bloomberg.net  